{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260429/s00024/8b0a69c1cb37438dac6f12df1efae216.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>天文台發出特別天氣提示，位於珠江口一帶的強雷雨區正逐漸向東發展，預料未來兩三小時本港驟雨逐漸增多，下午雨勢有時頗大。市民請留意天氣變化。（天文台）</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T02:37:45.621811+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":73,"images":1,"source":"明報 消閒","fallback":"none"}}